{"tid":1117790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（拋磚引玉）一齊講下主權移交後 被支共醜化嘅港英歷史","createTime":"2019-04-21T03:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T14:02:38.000Z","uid":18245,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"29f8164a5ed4eca3674dd97ffddb00f12e6bbe19","tid":1117790,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"先講嘅係The Sino&ndash;British Joint Declaration 中文係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">英中聯合聲明</span></span>  類似嘅「中港問題」呢啲字眼都係為咗貶低香港同香港人。 香港人係應該講「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港中問題</span></span>」<br />\n同樣用漢字嘅國家日本用嘅係「<strong>英中</strong>共同声明」、「<strong>日米</strong>和親条約」 etc. <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk.emb-japan.go.jp/jp/docs/hk_macau.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk.emb-japan.go.jp%2Fjp%2Fdocs%2Fhk_macau.pdf&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=455530cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk.emb-japan.go.jp/jp/docs/hk_macau.pdf</a><br />\n<strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">港英政府肯推德政係多得六七暴動</div></strong><br />\n1967年 由支共策劃嘅六七暴動<br />\n支共當年係直頭派兵喺沙頭角越境，射殺5名香港警員。之後仲散播搖言話中共就快會「解放」香港，慫恿當年香港嘅親共份子去搞暴動。呢班仆街係香港街頭放真假炸彈，<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2個香港人身亡</span></span></strong></span>（一個7歲女童同佢嘅2歲細佬）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VFdb1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VFdb1k.jpg&h=8d2e3d36&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n當年有個商業電台主持林彬睇唔過眼，開咪屌鳩班仆街，最後比支那派人連人帶車燒至重傷不治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mamozg4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmamozg4.png&h=6d5eebcc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暴動期間，造成至少52人死亡，其後支共企圖將責任推比港英政府話如果冇呢次暴動，港英政府唔會推行往後嘅德政如：免費教育。但事實港英政府係1965年嘅教育白皮書已經晨早講咗會推免費教育。<br />\n<br />\n五毛唔該出返去！"},{"pid":"70bffe37ca1d4fc037b4f1936cd504b635e43fad","tid":1117790,"uid":33028,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"點解英文都係Sino行先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b27ed4f5ae615e0bbcd1020f4a8038b50180228","tid":1117790,"uid":41308,"like":1,"dislike":49,"score":-48,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"六七暴動起因係被英國逼害<br />\n過多十年，六七暴動變六七起義 無死過一個人"},{"pid":"021b278b1b6c932dbf07dbc0886394c998474af7","tid":1117790,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"70bffe37ca1d4fc037b4f1936cd504b635e43fad","tid":1117790,"uid":33028,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"點解英文都係Sino行先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"點解用sino唔用china?"},{"pid":"f00c0cadc02969d109cdb215008f45d0070cdde9","tid":1117790,"uid":27411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b27ed4f5ae615e0bbcd1020f4a8038b50180228","tid":1117790,"uid":41308,"like":1,"dislike":49,"score":-48,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"六七暴動起因係被英國逼害<br />\n過多十年，六七暴動變六七起義 無死過一個人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"到時仲會好似廣州「起義」南昌「起義」咁，直頭起個烈士陵園同紀念塔紀念班暴徒"},{"pid":"bcc1a3827259c6ab9bd314b64d975f0909d105b3","tid":1117790,"uid":33028,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"其實英中定中英唔算係貶低，當年香港政府都係用中英<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CfLMxgb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCfLMxgb.jpg&h=a197432f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8334f07f0ad4c9558929b640e79229910cdae6df","tid":1117790,"uid":27411,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:52:28.000Z","msg":"其實政府正式文件已經冇用「中港關係」好耐啦，改用「內地與香港的關係」之類更加煽情既字眼"},{"pid":"83323d41aa9d29635cc76c9c78b1561d2aa8d21d","tid":1117790,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f00c0cadc02969d109cdb215008f45d0070cdde9","tid":1117790,"uid":27411,"like":0,"dislike"